    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Chronic\nheadache\nNausea and vomiting\nFever\nNuchal rigidity\nAltered mental status\nSeizure\nSpinal cord compression (non-traumatic)\nLimb weakness\nDermatomal sensory loss\nRadicular pain\nBladder and bowel dysfunction\nCranial nerve abnormalities\nDiplopia\nFacial weakness\nHearing loss\nAtaxia",
